From a large collection out of Chicago, we are pleased to offer this gorgeous 1994/1995 Fender '62 Reissue Telecaster in Candy Apple Red, serial# S098868. This Tele is an Ash double-bound body that weighs approximately 7lbs 9oz. The condition of this piece is pretty great. Its one and only owner played and loved it, but took incredible care of all of their pieces. There is a small chip/ding in the paint/binding on the back left bout, but nothing to write home about. The neck is Maple with a Rosewood fretboard with lots of life on it! The nut measures 1 11/16" with a fretboard radius of 10". Electronically, our '62 Reissue has two single pups with three-way pick up selector switch, volume & control knobs. The Tele comes with a gig bag.
